ada–United States–Mexico Agreement, and analysis of major elections show these standalone pieces as components of a cohesive body of political commentary.In these last four years, everything happened at high speed. Politics & Players ably navigates the terrain.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aPoliticianszCanadaxHistoryy21st century. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / Canadian.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780228012139?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780228012139423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780228012139/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles